{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"64986-the-adventures-of-akara-and-linio","title":"The Adventures of Akara and Linio","description":"Akara is a standing line. Linio is a sleeping line. The two friends go out to play with their other line friends. What do you think happens? ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Kuzhali  Manickavel "],"illustrators":["Aindri C"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/64986-the-adventures-of-akara-and-linio"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715539/size3/cf9d88b7013979cf37ea1f9bb0c93c9c.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/715539/size6/cf9d88b7013979cf37ea1f9bb0c93c9c.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106234/size6/31026d90335fd23c08b8b63d61cce997.jpg","text":"Meet Akara and Linio. They are straight lines.\nAkara is a standing line.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106224/size6/bfda523114f22c49a8b50bcecd61bb47.jpg","text":"Linio is a sleeping line.\nCome on, let’s meet some of their other line friends!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106306/size6/312b405b3691dd4a1722714ba7acdc83.jpg","text":"See these curved lines? They are Archit and Squiggles.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106226/size6/936270a60ed6d03b36205332b67ab684.jpg","text":"This is Slopes! Slopes is a slanting line.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106307/size6/4c9d7de485f9f2a54181f1f5f662a17a.jpg","text":"What are these friends going to do today?\nThey are going to make animal shapes together.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106228/size6/9c8018cb8c9f2c43c2a2017071ce7dc2.jpg","text":"Look at this dog! Can you spot Linio?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106229/size6/57cabdf74a2f38fcbf2b5d0448b59f7c.jpg","text":"Wow, look at this elephant! Where is Archit, can you see?","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106230/size6/24f74cd39df2d2c6b86da046f149cc53.jpg","text":"Hey, it’s a turtle! Can you spot Squiggles?","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106231/size6/d94b1e3573c7a872ea173babb3f606ae.jpg","text":"What a lovely snail! And there’s Slopes, can you see?","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106232/size6/645176b8b1f9302c1f4a768388feaf1e.jpg","text":"Woohoo, an owl! Where’s Akara?","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/106237/size6/303d0933caaaf5c7d3ebf4b433a85b1e.jpg","text":"Shhh! The lines are all resting now.\nMaking animal shapes is fun, but tiring!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":117}}